commentary: Root to de Kock, OUT bowled 'im! Ding, ding, ding...! Root rattles the woodwork, those magic lollipops working the trick for England! commentary: Jordan to Bavuma, OUT full and staying a touch low, hit on the back pad... Jordan appeals and Aleem Dar shakes his head, but England review, and this doesn't look good for Bavuma. Thudding into leg stump, according to Hawk-Eye, and that is curtains!. Up goes Dar's finger, and then immediately he signals to the groundsmen, too! It's raining again!
